PHP-Push is a fork of z-push with combined backends:
Mail: IMAP
Calendar: CalDAV
Contacts: LDAP

Now i have adpted the Package that pho-push also works on Lighttp
The only alias you have to set is:

alias.url= ( "/Microsoft-Server-ActiveSync"=> "/path/toyour/php-push/index.php")

Also thanks to Marco from https://www.forgetaboutit.net/software/ for a big part of the code!
